<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Outside" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Outside,</orth> 1) external part, surface: <cit><quote>the o. of his hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.834" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 834</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you look but on the o. of this work,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.109" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 2, 109</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.2.109" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 2, 109</bibl> <cit><quote>make his wrongs his --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 3.5.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 5, 33</bibl></cit> (not letting them enter the heart).<lb />2) exterior, external appearance, person: <bibl n="shak. mv 1.3.103" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 3, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.68" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.122" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.2.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 2, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.646" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 646</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.4.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 4, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.244" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 244</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 159</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.142" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.2.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 2, 50</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>